window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jaded veteran, badass arsenal, corrupt authority: a recipe for punishment.</p> <p>Meet Jack, a jaded vet from Earth. During the day he’s a nobody who is shunned and abused. However, at night he’ll grow to be an ungodly powerhouse that would put fear in the hearts of the rich and corrupt. He’ll use every bit of courage, and ingenuity to wreak vengeance on anyone who messes with him or his friends.</p> <p>And while his living is rough, there’s something more dreadful afoot. People vanish in the night. Portals are opening in the city, unleashing demons, and a great army approaches, seeking to conquer the land. Jack will have to act fast. He’ll need to face all manner of monsters to protect what’s his, yet the worst are not the demons outside the city walls.</p> <p>[Overpowered Badass MC] [LitRPG] [Isekai] [Steady Progression] [Void + Iron + Time abilities] [Fast Paced]</p> <p>*** Over 400,000 views on Royal Road ***</p>"; 
